      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "数学家真的给一类数起名叫做快乐数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "一个数快不快乐，取决于一场简单的迭代游戏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "rule-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/rule-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "规则是：把这个数每一位的数字都平方，再全部加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "rule-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/rule-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "比如 19，就是 1 的平方加 9 的平方，等于 82。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "rule-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/rule-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "得到的新数继续这样算，一步接着一步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "converge-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/converge-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "有的数一路走下去，最终会稳稳地停在 1，这就是快乐数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "converge-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/converge-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "19 就是这样：82、68、100，最后到 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "converge-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/converge-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "不快乐的数则会掉进一个固定的八数循环，永远出不来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "distribute",
      "line_id": "dis-1",
      "filename": "distribute-dis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/distribute-dis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "在 100 以内，快乐数大约有二十个，散落其间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "distribute",
      "line_id": "dis-2",
      "filename": "distribute-dis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/distribute-dis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "它们的分布看似杂乱，却藏着确定的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
